&lt;p&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;Commercial Maintenance Technician&lt;/strong&gt; is responsible for performing highly diversified duties to install, troubleshoot, repair and maintain property according to safety, predictive and productive maintenance systems and processes to support the achievement of the site&#39;s business goals and objectives.&amp;nbsp; This position supports the full portfolio for Van Metre Commercial, &lt;strong&gt;primarily servicing two sites in Fairfax, Virginia&lt;/strong&gt;. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
