&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Planning and undertaking scheduled maintenance at multiple properties throughout the portfolio.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Read and interpret equipment manuals and work orders to perform required maintenance and service.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plan and undertake scheduled maintenance at multiple properties throughout the portfolio.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform highly diversified duties to install and maintain property machines and equipment, including checking, repairing, and servicing machinery, equipment, systems, and infrastructure; diagnosing problems; replacing or repairing parts; testing; and making adjustments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform regular preventive maintenance on machines, equipment and plant facilities. Ensure the efficiency and reliability of mechanical equipment.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Detect faulty operations, defective material and report those and any unusual situations to proper supervision.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform a variety of plumbing maintenance and carpentry functions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use a variety of hand and power tools, electric meters and material handling equipment in performing duties.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with snow removal.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain parking lot cleanliness at various properties.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage supplies for assigned properties and coordinate with Facility Director and Property Manager.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee cleaning staff and report any findings to management.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in on call responsibilities on a rotational basis with two additional technicians.
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;While on call, this position will service all of our properties ranging between Winchester, VA and Arlington, VA.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform all other duties as assigned or needed.&lt;/li&gt;
